Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of spiritual experiences since I had mine, I've checked with other people
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and they said that it happens just as you're going off to sleep or just as you're coming awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when it usually you're awake enough to think, is this a dream or is this really happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was my experience.
