Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And this light force came in through the corner and it lit up the whole room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a brilliant light as though brighter than looking at the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And it had an energy behind the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
